{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Being a child, and sort of crawling around the house,"},{"time":2000,"text":"I remember these Turkish carpets,"},{"time":4000,"text":"and there were these scenes, these battle scenes, these love scenes."},{"time":9000,"text":"I mean, look, this animal is trying to fight back this spear"},{"time":14000,"text":"from this soldier."},{"time":15000,"text":"And my mom took these pictures actually, last week,"},{"time":18000,"text":"of our carpets, and I remember this to this day."},{"time":21000,"text":"There was another object, this sort of towering piece of furniture"},{"time":25000,"text":"with creatures and gargoyles and nudity --"},{"time":27000,"text":"pretty scary stuff, when you're a little kid."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"What I remember today from this is that objects tell stories,"},{"time":34000,"text":"so storytelling has been a really strong influence in my work."},{"time":42000,"text":"And then there was another influence."},{"time":43000,"text":"I was a teenager, and at 15 or 16, I guess like all teenagers,"},{"time":46000,"text":"we want to just do what we love and what we believe in."},{"time":49000,"text":"And so,"},{"time":52000,"text":"I fused together the two things I loved the most,"},{"time":54000,"text":"which was skiing and windsurfing."},{"time":57000,"text":"Those are pretty good escapes from the drab weather in Switzerland."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62000,"text":"So, I created this compilation of the two:"},{"time":65000,"text":"I took my skis and I took a board and I put a mast foot in there,"},{"time":69000,"text":"and some foot straps, and some metal fins,"},{"time":73000,"text":"and here I was, going really fast on frozen lakes."},{"time":76000,"text":"It was really a death trap. I mean, it was incredible,"},{"time":79000,"text":"it worked incredibly well, but it was really dangerous."},{"time":82000,"text":"And I realized then I had to go to design school."},{"time":86000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":87000,"text":"I mean, look at those graphics there."},{"time":89000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":92000,"text":"So, I went to design school,"},{"time":96000,"text":"and it was the early '90s when I finished."},{"time":101000,"text":"And I saw something extraordinary happening in Silicon Valley,"},{"time":105000,"text":"so I wanted to be there,"},{"time":106000,"text":"and I saw that the computer was coming into our homes,"},{"time":110000,"text":"that it had to change in order to be with us in our homes."},{"time":114000,"text":"And so I got myself a job and I was working for a consultancy,"},{"time":118000,"text":"and we would get in to these meetings,"},{"time":119000,"text":"and these managers would come in,"},{"time":122000,"text":"and they would say,"},{"time":124000,"text":"\"Well, what we're going to do here is really important, you know.\""},{"time":127000,"text":"And they would give the projects code names, you know,"},{"time":130000,"text":"mostly from \"Star Wars,\" actually: things like C3PO, Yoda, Luke."},{"time":138000,"text":"So, in anticipation, I would be this young designer"},{"time":141000,"text":"in the back of the room, and I would raise my hand,"},{"time":143000,"text":"and I would ask questions."},{"time":145000,"text":"I mean, in retrospect, probably stupid questions,"},{"time":148000,"text":"but things like, \"What's this Caps Lock key for?\""},{"time":152000,"text":"or \"What's this Num Lock key for?\" You know, that thing?"},{"time":157000,"text":"\"You know, do people really use it?"},{"time":158000,"text":"Do they need it? Do they want it in their homes?\""},{"time":161000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":164000,"text":"What I realized then is, they didn't really want to change"},{"time":169000,"text":"the legacy stuff; they didn't want to change the insides."},{"time":172000,"text":"They were really looking for us, the designers, to create the skins,"},{"time":182000,"text":"to put some pretty stuff outside of the box."},{"time":186000,"text":"And I didn't want to be a colorist."},{"time":188000,"text":"It wasn't what I wanted to do."},{"time":190000,"text":"I didn't want to be a stylist in this way."},{"time":192000,"text":"And then I saw this quote:"},{"time":194000,"text":"\"advertising is the price companies pay for being unoriginal.\""},{"time":199000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":202000,"text":"So, I had to start on my own. So I moved to San Francisco,"},{"time":205000,"text":"and I started a little company, fuseproject."},{"time":209000,"text":"And what I wanted to work on is important stuff."},{"time":211000,"text":"And I wanted to really not just work on the skins,"},{"time":216000,"text":"but I wanted to work on the entire human experience."},{"time":219000,"text":"And so the first projects were sort of humble,"},{"time":223000,"text":"but they took technology and maybe made it into things"},{"time":228000,"text":"that people would use in a new way,"},{"time":231000,"text":"and maybe finding some new functionality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":232000,"text":"This is a watch we made for Mini Cooper, the car company,"},{"time":236000,"text":"right when it launched,"},{"time":237000,"text":"and it's the first watch that has a display"},{"time":240000,"text":"that switches from horizontal to vertical."},{"time":242000,"text":"And that allows me to check my timer discretely, here,"},{"time":247000,"text":"without bending my elbow."},{"time":248000,"text":"And other projects, which were really about transformation,"},{"time":252000,"text":"about matching the human need."},{"time":255000,"text":"This is a little piece of furniture for an Italian manufacturer,"},{"time":258000,"text":"and it ships completely flat,"},{"time":260000,"text":"and then it folds into a coffee table and a stool and whatnot."},{"time":265000,"text":"And something a little bit more experimental:"},{"time":266000,"text":"this is a light fixture for Swarovski,"},{"time":270000,"text":"and what it does is, it changes shape."},{"time":272000,"text":"So, it goes from a circle, to a round, to a square, to a figure eight."},{"time":276000,"text":"And just by drawing on a little computer tablet,"},{"time":279000,"text":"the entire light fixture adjusts to what shape you want."}]},{"cues":[{"time":284000,"text":"And then finally, the leaf lamp for Herman Miller."},{"time":286000,"text":"This is a pretty involved process;"},{"time":288000,"text":"it took us about four and a half years."},{"time":290000,"text":"But I really was looking for creating a unique experience of light,"},{"time":295000,"text":"a new experience of light."},{"time":296000,"text":"So, we had to design both the light and the light bulb."},{"time":301000,"text":"And that's a unique opportunity, I would say, in design."},{"time":305000,"text":"And the new experience I was looking for"},{"time":307000,"text":"is giving the choice for the user to go from"},{"time":310000,"text":"a warm, sort of glowing kind of mood light,"},{"time":313000,"text":"all the way to a bright work light."},{"time":316000,"text":"So, the light bulb actually does that."},{"time":319000,"text":"It allows the person to switch,"},{"time":321000,"text":"and to mix these two colorations."},{"time":323000,"text":"And it's done in a very simple way:"},{"time":326000,"text":"one just touches the base of the light,"},{"time":329000,"text":"and on one side, you can mix the brightness,"},{"time":331000,"text":"and on the other, the coloration of the light."}]},{"cues":[{"time":334000,"text":"So, all of these projects have a humanistic sense to them,"},{"time":339000,"text":"and I think as designers we need to really think"},{"time":341000,"text":"about how we can create a different relationship"},{"time":345000,"text":"between our work and the world,"},{"time":348000,"text":"whether it's for business,"},{"time":349000,"text":"or, as I'm going to show, on some civic-type projects."},{"time":354000,"text":"Because I think everybody agrees that as designers we bring"},{"time":359000,"text":"value to business, value to the users also,"},{"time":364000,"text":"but I think it's the values that we put into these projects"},{"time":368000,"text":"that ultimately create the greater value."},{"time":372000,"text":"And the values we bring"},{"time":373000,"text":"can be about environmental issues,"},{"time":377000,"text":"about sustainability, about lower power consumption."},{"time":380000,"text":"You know, they can be about function and beauty;"},{"time":384000,"text":"they can be about business strategy."},{"time":385000,"text":"But designers are really the glue"},{"time":388000,"text":"that brings these things together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":390000,"text":"So Jawbone is a project that you're familiar with,"},{"time":396000,"text":"and it has a humanistic technology."},{"time":399000,"text":"It feels your skin. It rests on your skin,"},{"time":402000,"text":"and it knows when it is you're talking."},{"time":403000,"text":"And by knowing when it is you're talking,"},{"time":406000,"text":"it gets rid of the other noises that it knows about,"},{"time":408000,"text":"which is the environmental noises."}]},{"cues":[{"time":411000,"text":"But the other thing that is humanistic about Jawbone"},{"time":413000,"text":"is that we really decided to take out all the techie stuff,"},{"time":419000,"text":"and all the nerdy stuff out of it,"},{"time":421000,"text":"and try to make it as beautiful as we can."},{"time":423000,"text":"I mean, think about it:"},{"time":424000,"text":"the care we take in selecting sunglasses, or jewelry,"},{"time":431000,"text":"or accessories is really important,"},{"time":435000,"text":"so if it isn't beautiful, it really doesn't belong on your face."},{"time":439000,"text":"And this is what we're pursuing here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442000,"text":"But how we work on Jawbone is really unique."},{"time":446000,"text":"I want to point at something here, on the left."},{"time":448000,"text":"This is the board, this is one of the things that goes inside"},{"time":452000,"text":"that makes this technology work."},{"time":454000,"text":"But this is the design process:"},{"time":456000,"text":"there's somebody changing the board,"},{"time":457000,"text":"putting tracers on the board, changing the location of the ICs,"},{"time":461000,"text":"as the designers on the other side are doing the work."},{"time":464000,"text":"So, it's not about slapping skins, anymore, on a technology."},{"time":468000,"text":"It's really about designing from the inside out."},{"time":470000,"text":"And then, on the other side of the room,"},{"time":473000,"text":"the designers are making small adjustments,"},{"time":474000,"text":"sketching, drawing by hand, putting it in the computer."},{"time":479000,"text":"And it's what I call being design driven."},{"time":483000,"text":"You know, there is some push and pull,"},{"time":485000,"text":"but design is really helping define"},{"time":487000,"text":"the whole experience from the inside out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":491000,"text":"And then, of course, design is never done."},{"time":493000,"text":"And this is -- the other new way that is unique"},{"time":497000,"text":"in how we work is, because it's never done,"},{"time":499000,"text":"you have to do all this other stuff."},{"time":501000,"text":"The packaging, and the website, and you need to continue"},{"time":504000,"text":"to really touch the user, in many ways."},{"time":508000,"text":"But how do you retain somebody, when it's never done?"},{"time":512000,"text":"And Hosain Rahman, the CEO of Aliph Jawbone,"},{"time":519000,"text":"you know, really understands that you need a different structure."},{"time":522000,"text":"So, in a way, the different structure is that we're partners,"},{"time":526000,"text":"it's a partnership. We can continue to work"},{"time":531000,"text":"and dedicate ourselves to this project,"},{"time":534000,"text":"and then we also share in the rewards."}]},{"cues":[{"time":536000,"text":"And here's another project, another partnership-type approach."},{"time":541000,"text":"This is called Y Water,"},{"time":543000,"text":"and it's this guy from Los Angeles, Thomas Arndt,"},{"time":547000,"text":"Austrian originally, who came to us,"},{"time":549000,"text":"and all he wanted to do was to create a healthy drink,"},{"time":553000,"text":"or an organic drink for his kids,"},{"time":556000,"text":"to replace the high-sugar-content sodas"},{"time":560000,"text":"that he's trying to get them away from."},{"time":562000,"text":"So, we worked on this bottle,"},{"time":565000,"text":"and it's completely symmetrical in every dimension."},{"time":567000,"text":"And this allows the bottle to turn into a game."},{"time":574000,"text":"The bottles connect together,"},{"time":575000,"text":"and you can create different shapes, different forms."},{"time":579000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":580000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":582000,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":583000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":585000,"text":"And then while we were doing this,"},{"time":586000,"text":"the shape of the bottle upside down reminded us of a Y,"},{"time":590000,"text":"and then we thought, well these words, \"why\" and \"why not,\""},{"time":595000,"text":"are probably the most important words that kids ask."},{"time":598000,"text":"So we called it Y Water. And so this is"},{"time":601000,"text":"another place where it all comes together in the same room:"},{"time":604000,"text":"the three-dimensional design, the ideas, the branding,"},{"time":610000,"text":"it all becomes deeply connected."},{"time":613000,"text":"And then the other thing about this project is,"},{"time":615000,"text":"we bring intellectual property,"},{"time":619000,"text":"we bring a marketing approach,"},{"time":621000,"text":"we bring all this stuff, but I think, at the end of the day,"},{"time":623000,"text":"what we bring is these values,"},{"time":625000,"text":"and these values create a soul for the companies we work with."},{"time":629000,"text":"And it's especially rewarding when your design work"},{"time":630000,"text":"becomes a creative endeavor,"},{"time":633000,"text":"when others can be creative and do more with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":635000,"text":"Here's another project,"},{"time":636000,"text":"which I think really emulates that."},{"time":639000,"text":"This is the One Laptop per Child, the $100 laptop."},{"time":646000,"text":"This picture is incredible."},{"time":647000,"text":"In Nigeria, people carry their most precious belongings on their heads."},{"time":653000,"text":"This girl is going to school with a laptop on her head."},{"time":655000,"text":"I mean, to me, it just means so much."},{"time":659000,"text":"But when Nicholas Negroponte --"},{"time":661000,"text":"and he has spoken about this project a lot,"},{"time":663000,"text":"he's the founder of OLPC -- came to us"},{"time":668000,"text":"about two and a half years ago,"},{"time":672000,"text":"there were some clear ideas."},{"time":674000,"text":"He wanted to bring education and he wanted to bring technology,"},{"time":678000,"text":"and those are pillars of his life,"},{"time":679000,"text":"but also pillars of the mission of One Laptop per Child."},{"time":685000,"text":"But the third pillar that he talked about was design."},{"time":689000,"text":"And at the time, I wasn't really working on computers."},{"time":693000,"text":"I didn't really want to, from the previous adventure."},{"time":695000,"text":"But what he said was really significant,"},{"time":698000,"text":"is that design was going to be why the kids"},{"time":700000,"text":"were going to love this product,"},{"time":702000,"text":"how we were going to make it low cost, robust."},{"time":704000,"text":"And plus, he said he was going to get rid of the Caps Lock key --"},{"time":711000,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":713000,"text":"and the Num Lock key, too."}]},{"cues":[{"time":715000,"text":"So, I was convinced. We designed it to be iconic,"},{"time":719000,"text":"to look different. To look like it's for a kid, but not like a toy."},{"time":725000,"text":"And then the integration of"},{"time":727000,"text":"all these great technologies, which you've heard about,"},{"time":730000,"text":"the Wi-Fi antennas that allow the kids to connect;"},{"time":733000,"text":"the screen, which you can read in sunlight;"},{"time":737000,"text":"the keyboard, which is made out of rubber,"},{"time":739000,"text":"and it's protected from the environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":741000,"text":"You know, all these great technologies really happened"},{"time":744000,"text":"because of the passion and"},{"time":748000,"text":"the OLPC people and the engineers."},{"time":751000,"text":"They fought the suppliers,"},{"time":753000,"text":"they fought the manufacturers."},{"time":757000,"text":"I mean, they fought like animals"},{"time":761000,"text":"for this to remain they way it is."},{"time":763000,"text":"And in a way, it is that will that makes projects like this one --"},{"time":770000,"text":"allows the process"},{"time":771000,"text":"from not destroying the original idea."},{"time":774000,"text":"And I think this is something really important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":776000,"text":"So, now you get these pictures --"},{"time":779000,"text":"you get up in the morning, and you see the kids in Nigeria"},{"time":782000,"text":"and you see them in Uruguay"},{"time":784000,"text":"with their computers, and in Mongolia."},{"time":788000,"text":"And we went away from obviously the beige."},{"time":791000,"text":"I mean it's colorful, it's fun."},{"time":792000,"text":"In fact, you can see each logo is a little bit different."},{"time":797000,"text":"It's because we were able"},{"time":799000,"text":"to run, during the manufacturing process,"},{"time":805000,"text":"20 colors for the X and the O,"},{"time":806000,"text":"which is the name of the computer,"},{"time":809000,"text":"and by mixing them on the manufacturing floor,"},{"time":812000,"text":"you get 20 times 20: you get"},{"time":816000,"text":"400 different options there."},{"time":818000,"text":"So, the lessons from seeing the kids"},{"time":820000,"text":"using them in the developing world are incredible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":822000,"text":"But this is my nephew, Anthony, in Switzerland,"},{"time":826000,"text":"and he had the laptop for an afternoon,"},{"time":828000,"text":"and I had to take it back. It was hard."},{"time":831000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":832000,"text":"And it was a prototype. And a month and a half later,"},{"time":836000,"text":"I come back to Switzerland,"},{"time":837000,"text":"and there he is playing with his own version."},{"time":843000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":844000,"text":"Like paper, paper and cardboard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":849000,"text":"So, I'm going to finish with one last project,"},{"time":854000,"text":"and this is a little bit more of adult play."},{"time":857000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":858000,"text":"Some of you might have heard about the New York City condom."},{"time":862000,"text":"It's actually just launched, actually launched on Valentine's Day,"},{"time":867000,"text":"February 14, about 10 days ago."},{"time":870000,"text":"So, the Department of Health in New York came to us,"},{"time":874000,"text":"and they needed a way to distribute"},{"time":879000,"text":"36 million condoms for free to the citizens of New York."},{"time":884000,"text":"So a pretty big endeavor, and we worked on the dispensers."},{"time":889000,"text":"These are the dispensers. There's this friendly shape."},{"time":892000,"text":"It's a little bit like designing a fire hydrant,"},{"time":897000,"text":"and it has to be easily serviceable:"},{"time":902000,"text":"you have to know where it is and what it does."},{"time":905000,"text":"And we also designed the condoms themselves."}]},{"cues":[{"time":910000,"text":"And I was just in New York at the launch,"},{"time":912000,"text":"and I went to see all these places where they're installed:"},{"time":915000,"text":"this is at a Puerto Rican little mom-and-pop store;"},{"time":920000,"text":"at a bar in Christopher Street; at a pool hall."},{"time":924000,"text":"I mean, they're being installed in homeless clinics -- everywhere."},{"time":927000,"text":"Of course, clubs and discos, too."},{"time":931000,"text":"And here's the public service announcement for this project."},{"time":933000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":948000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":949000,"text":"Get some."},{"time":951000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":957000,"text":"So, this is really where design"},{"time":961000,"text":"is able to create a conversation."},{"time":962000,"text":"I was in these venues, and people were,"},{"time":965000,"text":"you know, really into getting them. They were excited."},{"time":968000,"text":"It was breaking the ice,"},{"time":973000,"text":"it was getting over a stigma,"},{"time":975000,"text":"and I think that's also what design can do."},{"time":979000,"text":"So, I was going to"},{"time":980000,"text":"throw some condoms in the room and whatnot,"},{"time":984000,"text":"but I'm not sure it's the etiquette here."},{"time":988000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":989000,"text":"Yeah? All right, all right. I have only a few."},{"time":991000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":994000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":997000,"text":"So, I have more, you can always ask me for some more later."},{"time":1004000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":1005000,"text":"And if anybody asks why you're carrying a condom,"},{"time":1009000,"text":"you can just say you like the design."},{"time":1010000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1014000,"text":"So, I'll finish with just one thought:"},{"time":1016000,"text":"if we all work together on creating value,"},{"time":1020000,"text":"but if we really keep in mind the values of the work that we do,"},{"time":1024000,"text":"I think we can change the work that we do."},{"time":1030000,"text":"We can change these values, can change the companies we work with,"},{"time":1033000,"text":"and eventually, together, maybe we can change the world."},{"time":1038000,"text":"So, thank you."},{"time":1039000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}